import React from 'react'
import Carousel from 'react-elastic-carousel'
import Item from './Item'

const Carrousel = ({Item}) => {
  return (
        <Carousel itemsToShow={1}>
            <Item>1</Item>
            <Item>2</Item>
            <Item>3</Item>
            <Item>4</Item>
            <Item>5</Item>
            <Item>6</Item>
        </Carousel>
  )
}

export default Carrousel
